43 |  game_concept_beaded_crown_desc:0 "The ruler of $c_ife$, called the Ooni, had and has great religious and secular authority among the Yoruba peoples. Historically, monarchs in the region would travel to $c_ife$ to be crowned by the Ooni with the special beaded crown of Oduduwa, a deity and progenitor of various Yoruba and Edo kings, to legitimize their rule.\n\nIn-game, the Ooni serves as the [head_of_faith|E] of the $west_african_orisha_pagan$ [faith|E]. [rulers|E] who follow a [faith|E] of the $west_african_orisha_religion$ [religion|E], or those in the region who meet other requirements, can take the [decision|E] travel to $c_ife$ to $RICE_niger_delta_request_beaded_crown$. After you select a gift to offer the Ooni, they will decide whether to accept it or reject the gift. If you are the Ooni yourself, you can receive gifts and crown [rulers|E] conversely.\n\nIf you follow a [faith|E] of the $west_african_orisha_religion$ [religion|E], you will be stuck with the [GetModifier('RICE_niger_delta_uncrowned').GetNameWithTooltip] [character_modifier|E] until you get the Ooni to agree to crown you."
   |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ 

