282 |  RICE_tarim_basin_khotan_procession_monastery_type_mashe_desc: "$EFFECT_LIST_BULLET$In preparation for the procession, you will donate to Mashe Monastery, which has legendary associations with Khotan's silk industry.\n$EFFECT_LIST_BULLET$Increases the cost of this [activity|E] by [gold_i|E]#V [GetPlayer.MakeScope.ScriptValue('RICE_tarim_basin_khotan_mashe_donation_cost')]#!\n$EFFECT_LIST_BULLET$Gain [prestige_i|E] #V 100#! at the end of this [activity|E].\n\n#weak According to legend, silk was brought to Khotan thanks to a Chinese princess, and Mashe Monastery was built on the site where she planted mulberry trees. As such, the monastery is well-respected in the region, and deserves our support.#!"
    |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ 

