259 |  RICE_sri_lanka_pali_literature_grammatical_aid_desc:0 "$RICE_sri_lanka_pali_literature_basic$This text is a treatise designed to assist the reader with learning and mastering the grammar of highly esteemed languages used widely in certain Buddhist sects, particularly Pali or Sanskrit. According to this text, mastery of these languages is not only an intellectual matter, but one of spiritual development as well, for it allows one to understand the religious and philosophical background of sacred texts and commentaries written in these languages."
