474 |  game_concept_abhayagiri_desc:0 "The Abhayagiri, alongside the [mahavihara|E] and [jetavana|E], are one of the three major [RICE_sri_lanka_monasteries|E] in the [RICE_sri_lanka_struggle|E], or its Buddhist community. In-game, the Abhayagiri are represented by an yellow icon: @RICE_abhayagiri_icon!.\n\nYou can raise or lower the [RICE_sri_lanka_prominence|E] of the Abhayagiri through different [decisions|E], [activities|E], and so on, especially if you have the [GetTrait('RICE_abhayagiri_trait').GetName( GetNullCharacter )] [trait|E], which can be gained by taking the [decision|E] to $RICE_sri_lanka_choose_monastic_sect$. Keep this in mind if you wish to end the [struggle|E] in [RICE_sri_lanka_short|E].\n\nHistorically, the Abhayagiri were the more innovative monastery or sect of ancient and medieval Sri Lankan Buddhism. They often incorporated ideas from the Mahayana and Vajrayana varieties of Buddhism into the Theravada form of Buddhism practiced on Sri Lanka. At one point, they were the largest major monastery on the island."
    |                                                                 ^^^^^^^^^^ 

