893 |  RICE_sri_lanka_persecute_monastery_burn_books_option_tooltip:0 "$EFFECT_LIST_BULLET$Gain a random amount between [gold_i|E] #V #Bold [GetPlayer.MakeScope.ScriptValue('RICE_sri_lanka_minor_persecute_gold_gain_min')|0]#!#! and [gold_i|E] #V #Bold [GetPlayer.MakeScope.ScriptValue('RICE_sri_lanka_minor_persecute_gold_gain_max')|0]#!#!\n$EFFECT_LIST_BULLET$Lose [prestige_i|E] #V 100#!, and an extra [piety_i|E] #V 200#! if you are of a Buddhist [faith|E]\n$EFFECT_LIST_BULLET$Gain a [modifier|E] that increases [dread|E], reduces Buddhists' [opinions|E], and either decreases [prestige_i|E] [prestige|E], decreases [piety_i|E] [piety|E], or increases [piety_i|E] [piety|E] depending on if you are Buddhist or not and the current [struggle_phase|E] the [RICE_sri_lanka_struggle|E] is in\n$EFFECT_LIST_BULLET$[RICE_sri_lanka_monasteries|E] on the island lose #V [GetPlayer.MakeScope.ScriptValue('RICE_sri_lanka_prominence_loss_minor')|0]#! [RICE_sri_lanka_prominence|E], except if you are patronizing one\n$EFFECT_LIST_BULLET$Every [county|E] you own in [GetGeographicalRegion('RICE_sri_lanka_struggle_region').GetName] gains [control_i|E]#P [GetPlayer.MakeScope.ScriptValue('RICE_sri_lanka_persecute_control_gain_minor')|0]#! [control|E] and loses [development_i|E]#N [GetPlayer.MakeScope.ScriptValue('RICE_sri_lanka_persecute_development_loss_minor')|0]#! [development|E] progress"
    |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ 

