1022 |  sri_lanka.0005.desc:0 "$sri_lanka.0005.desc.intro$Recently, [sri_lanka_struggle_ender.GetTitledFirstName] has used [sri_lanka_struggle_ender.GetHerHis] authority to call a religious council to settle this issue once and for all, and to unite the island’s Sangha under the #bold [sri_lanka_struggle_ender.Custom('RICE_sri_lanka_patronized_monastery')]#!. All monastics must now adhere to [sri_lanka_struggle_ender.Custom('RICE_sri_lanka_patronized_monastery')] doctrines and practices, or be castigated as heretics. The #bold [GetPlayer.Custom('RICE_sri_lanka_unified_sangha_relic')] #!has also been affirmed as the relic par excellence of the island, a symbol of its newfound unity.\n\n"
