1023 |  sri_lanka.0005.desc.buddhist:0 "[sri_lanka_struggle_ender.GetFirstNameNoTooltip] claims [sri_lanka_struggle_ender.GetSheHe] used [sri_lanka_struggle_ender.GetHerHis] authority as a mighty [sri_lanka_struggle_ender.GetFaith.GetAdjective] [sri_lanka_struggle_ender.GetTitleAsNameNoTooltip] to reform the Sangha, but in truth, the [sri_lanka_struggle_ender.Custom('RICE_sri_lanka_patronized_monastery')] had grown in prominence in recent years, so it was only a matter of time."
