1024 |  sri_lanka.0005.desc.non_buddhist:0 "[sri_lanka_struggle_ender.GetFirstNameNoTooltip], while not a [sri_lanka_struggle_ender.GetFaith.GetAdjective] [sri_lanka_struggle_ender.GetTitleAsNameNoTooltip], sees the value of working with the influential [sri_lanka_struggle_ender.Custom('RICE_sri_lanka_patronized_monastery')] to reform the Sangha."
