1140 |  sri_lanka.0030.desc.almsgiving:0 "Giving alms to monks is practiced regularly by many who follow the [buddhism.GetAdjective] teachings, and even those who do not, from the lowliest peasant to a mighty [ROOT.Char.GetTitleAsNameNoTooltip] such as myself. It is said that one gains great merit in doing so. While I have given my fair share of alms, I want to give a great donation of food to the monks of [GetPlayer.Custom('RICE_sri_lanka_sangha_location')], much larger than usual."
     |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ 

warning(missing-item): custom localization RICE_sri_lanka_sangha_location not defined in common/customizable_localization/
    --> [MOD] localization\replace\english\RICE_sri_lanka_l_english.yml
1141 |  sri_lanka.0030.desc.gavu_pillars:0 "I have ordered the construction of some new #italic gavu#! pillars, or #italic gavukanu#!, and repairs to existing ones in my territories in [GetPlayer.Custom('RICE_sri_lanka_sangha_location')]. These wayside stone pillars mark distances at regular intervals, and help travelers have a safe and quick journey, particularly pilgrims who seek to go to and from the island’s many religious sites. I and the monasteries I patronize can also inscribe political and religious messages onto them, to bring ourselves glory and recognition."
     |                                                                                                                                                                                                      ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ 

warning(missing-item): custom localization RICE_sri_lanka_sangha_location not defined in common/customizable_localization/
    --> [MOD] localization\replace\english\RICE_sri_lanka_l_english.yml
1142 |  sri_lanka.0030.desc.ritual_deposits:0 "Ritual deposits like the one I’m planning are a common [buddhism.GetAdjectiveNoTooltip] practice on [GetPlayer.Custom('RICE_sri_lanka_sangha_location')], and strongly associated with the powerful monasteries here like the [GetPlayer.Custom('RICE_sri_lanka_patronized_monastery')]. By burying items like holy texts, sacred objects, and more at the monastery or temple I have chosen, many believe one can enhance the spiritual power of its location, and gain much merit."
     |                                                                                                                                                                ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ 

