1143 |  sri_lanka.0030.desc.ambalamas:0 "I have ordered for the construction of several new #italic ambalamas#! in my territories in [GetPlayer.Custom('RICE_sri_lanka_sangha_location')], and renovation of existing ones. These deceptively simple rest-houses have been used for centuries by travelers, and have been strongly associated with pilgrims who seek to go to one of the island’s many religious sites. Thanks to this, the roads will be safer for those who wish to honor the Buddha, practice the Dharma, and elevate the Sangha."
     |                                                                                                                                                  ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ 

