1144 |  sri_lanka.0030.desc.ordination_ceremonies:0 "The monastic communities of [GetPlayer.Custom('RICE_sri_lanka_sangha_location')] are always bringing in new novice monks and nuns who aspire to use their human lifetime to practice the Buddha’s teachings and work towards enlightenment. I seek to sponsor the ordination ceremonies of some monks and nuns in [GetPlayer.Custom('RICE_sri_lanka_sangha_location')]. Having more of them around can only be a good thing."
     |                                                                                              ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ 

