1296 |  sri_lanka.0070.desc:0 "Today, I start my journey to [GetPlayer.Custom('RICE_sri_pada')]. It will be an arduous journey, traveling through miles and miles of wilderness, not to mention the actual mountain itself which will be quite difficult to climb. However, it will be well worth it.\n\n[GetPlayer.Custom('RICE_sri_pada')] is the holiest mountain in [GetGeographicalRegion('RICE_sri_lanka_alt_region').GetName]. In fact, it is so holy that people of all religions, not just [ROOT.Char.GetFaith.GetAdherentNamePlural], go on pilgrimage there.\n\nThe site's main attraction is a large foot print at the summit, which is said to have been made by [GetPlayer.Custom('RICE_sri_pada_footprint_person')] according to the [ROOT.Char.GetFaith.GetAdjectiveNoTooltip] [ROOT.Char.Custom('DefaultPriestTitlePlural')]. Visiting it is surely a great way to show my devotion to [ROOT.Char.GetFaith.HighGodName]!"
     |                                                                         ^^^^^^^^^^^^^ 

warning(missing-item): custom localization RICE_sri_pada not defined in common/customizable_localization/
    --> [MOD] localization\replace\english\RICE_sri_lanka_l_english.yml
