1331 |  sri_lanka.0080.desc:0 "One of the most fascinating things about [GetPlayer.Custom('RICE_sri_pada')] that I notice more and more, now that I am here, is that the site is honored by followers of many different creeds, not just [ROOT.Char.GetFaith.GetAdherentNamePlural].\n\nFor instance, there are followers of other faiths who call the mountain [GetPlayer.Custom('RICE_sri_pada_opp')], instead of [GetPlayer.Custom('RICE_sri_pada')] as we do. Not everyone believes [GetPlayer.Custom('RICE_sri_pada_footprint_person')] made the footprint at the mountain’s peak either.\n\nDespite this, and despite the fact there are still plenty of tensions between the various groups here, it is fascinating if not inspiring for some to see so people of many beliefs, including those who would normally be at blows with each other, share this sacred space."
     |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 ^^^^^^^^^^^^^ 

