1334 |  sri_lanka.0081.desc:0 "Around the vicinity of [GetPlayer.Custom('RICE_sri_pada')], and on [GetPlayer.Custom('RICE_sri_pada')] itself, it is common for people to avoid eating the meat of animals, or at least many of those who are followers of various [buddhism.GetAdjective] and [hinduism.GetAdjective] sects do. Even those that don’t reduce their consumption of meat, for it is said to allow one to better focus on the pilgrimage and veneration of [ROOT.Char.GetFaith.HighGodName]."
     |                                                                   ^^^^^^^^^^^^^ 

