1562 |  sri_lanka.0150.desc:0 "$sri_lanka.0150.pattini_games_intro$I heard that the horn game, #italic ankeliya#!, was recently played in a prominent village in [county.GetNameNoTier]. Both teams have a horn attached to a tree, and must use a rope to try to break the horn. The team that does this first is, of course, the winner."
