1572 |  sri_lanka.0152.desc:0 "I recently attended a ceremony of offerings to local milk-mothers. This traditional [ROOT.Char.GetCulture.GetName] event involves seven local women who take on the role of the goddess [GetPlayer.Custom('RICE_pattini')] during the ceremony. They are chosen based on fulfilling certain criteria, such as being virtuous and having good morals.\n\nDuring the ceremony, the women are given food rich in milk, and transformed thusly into “milk-mothers.” It is said that venerating [GetPlayer.Custom('RICE_pattini')] this way will assist one with any issues related to fertility and children, as well as one’s life in general."
     |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ^^^^^^^^^^^^ 

