1594 |  sri_lanka.0158.desc:0 "Though I am a supporter of the [ROOT.Char.Custom('RICE_sri_lanka_patronized_monastery')] monastery, I still need to do my duties as [ROOT.Char.GetTitleAsNameNoTooltip] and sometimes sponsor or work with other major [ROOT.Char.GetFaith.GetReligion.GetAdjective] monasteries and sects in my territories on the island of [GetGeographicalRegion('RICE_sri_lanka_alt_region').GetName].\n\nHowever, there are some staunch [ROOT.Char.Custom('RICE_sri_lanka_patronized_monastery')] monastics who claim that associating with those they consider heretics is ill-advised at best, and the same as indulging in heresy oneself at worst. These hardliners say I should avoid association with the other monasteries as often as I can."
     |                                                                           ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ 

